=== RAW MODEL ANSWER ===
Answer: Step 1: 5-Bromonicotinic acid → activate as the acid chloride with SOCl2 (or equivalent) and amidate with methylamine to give 5-bromo-N-methylnicotinamide. | Step 2: Obtain the matching brominated heterobicycle, 6-bromo-2-chloro-3-methyl-fused aza-quinazolin-4-one (same N-methyl, ring carbonyl, and ring Cl as in the target). | Step 3: Install the chlorophenyl linker by selective Suzuki coupling of the step-2 heteroaryl partner with 1-bromo-2-chloro-4-iodobenzene at the iodide, giving 6-(4-bromo-2-chlorophenyl)-2-chloro-3-methyl-fused aza-quinazolin-4-one. | Step 4: Miyaura borylation of the remaining aryl bromide (B2pin2, Pd, base) to form 6-(3-chloro-4-boronophenyl)-2-chloro-3-methyl-fused aza-quinazolin-4-one (pinacol boronate or boronic acid). | Step 5: Final Suzuki coupling of this boronated intermediate with 5-bromo-N-methylnicotinamide furnishes the exact target, CNC(=O)c1cc(-c2ccc(-c3cc4cnc(Cl)nc4n(C)c3=O)c(Cl)c2)ccn1.

